text: Vida Gerbec (born 1922, date of death unknown) was a Slovenian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Slovenian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
